
*User roles*

- Admin
- Teacher
- Student

*Core Modules*

> Authentication
    - Log in/out
    - Role-based access control
> User management
    • Admin
        - Add/remove/edit teacher/student
        - reset PIN
> Courses
    • Teacher
        - Create courses
    • Student
        - Enroll courses
> Grade
    • Teacher
        - Assign grades
    • Student
        - Check grades
